title: 'Survivor,' Season 42, Episode 4 With Sophie Clarke
description:
Riley and Juliet are joined by 'Survivor: South Pacific' winner and 'Survivor: Winners at War' contestant, Sophie Clarke. They break down another incredible challenge performance from Jonathan and how Tori was able to survive the tribal council. Plus, Sophie talks about how the show has changed since she was first on it and they hand out this week's superlatives. 
Hosts: Riley McAtee and Juliet Litman 
Guest: Sophie Clarke 
Production: Carlos Chiriboga
